- **Honeypot fields** (invisible, no user interaction)
- **Time-based delays** (e.g., disable submit for 5 seconds, visible countdown)
- **Non-distorted image selection** (e.g., “Select all images with bicycles”)
- **OTP/TOTP/magic links/passkeys** — all pass SC 3.3.8 as they avoid distortion entirely

