- Ensure the toggle is persistent (e.g., not hidden behind hover or focus)

Example HTML:
```html
<div class="password-field">
  <input type="password" id="pwd" autocomplete="current-password">
  <button type="button" aria-pressed="false" aria-label="Show password">
